title: Ryômen Sukuna
episode_desc: As Itadori cares for his grandpa, Fushiguro worries that he's carrying a cursed object of rare power. The Occult club messes with something far beyond their understanding.
show_desc: A boy swallows a cursed talisman - the finger of a demon - and becomes cursed himself. He enters a shaman's school to be able to locate the demon's other body parts and thus exorcise himself.

Either, he can be executed immediately or hunt down all fingers of Ryoumen Sakuna and be executed after ingesting them.
